{"tid":1050784,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"材質不折衷！iPhone 玻璃供應商：數年內準備好可摺疊玻璃","createTime":"2019-03-07T06:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T11:42:58.000Z","uid":109383,"like":15,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6aaf325f817770880aabb759f9e63667dc60c0","tid":1050784,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"現在市面上推出摺疊手機的廠商，包括 Samsung 和華為皆採用塑料聚合物為主的材質，以實現摺疊功能。然而，很難想像 Apple 會為了讓手機摺疊而在用料上折衷，畢竟該材質實際上還有不少問題。現在康寧公司則向外媒 CNBC 證實他們已著手研發「可彎曲玻璃產品」。<br />\n<br />\n採用塑料為主的摺疊手機本身在耐用度上遠不及玻璃，不僅容易刮傷表面，壽命也比較短，甚至是測試塑料螢幕的人員亦表示該材質還有有待解決的問題。<br />\n<br />\nApple 本身則是在 2017 年 5 月承諾為康寧的研發、主要設備和玻璃加工資助 2 億美元的資金。現在根據 Wired 的報導，康寧公司正在開發厚度僅 0.1mm 的可彎曲玻璃，使其可進行半徑 5mm 的摺疊。康寧公司的 John Bayne 表示他預期可摺疊的玻璃能夠在未來數年內準備好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />apple又比錢人洗"},{"pid":"9e68f680f550678ade9e7daad4f18da970163b7d","tid":1050784,"uid":89514,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"656dba440ec1e78c1be0741946e9e1a506918669","tid":1050784,"uid":62506,"like":18,"dislike":19,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:24:44.000Z","msg":"數年內<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地今年就出啦"},{"pid":"d7f77b6f04d4f73c977d907a545533635b51ccc0","tid":1050784,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"2皮野一部<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53bf8593ddd7032455079554c1bac3d88d97bfa","tid":1050784,"uid":39387,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"656dba440ec1e78c1be0741946e9e1a506918669","tid":1050784,"uid":62506,"like":18,"dislike":19,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:24:44.000Z","msg":"數年內<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地今年就出啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"唔係mon喎 講緊玻璃喎<br />\n依家samsung同華為都係膠面<br />\n好易花<br />\n唐寧係gorilla glass果間公司<br />\n依家係話整緊摺得埋既玻璃"},{"pid":"707723673c52918dc24ec2d473d903e489f20577","tid":1050784,"uid":39387,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"btw apple係好快會有摺mon既技術<br />\n因為apple有投資俾samsung研發個mon"},{"pid":"5486b09ce34b2bf386e9e4e0adc5759e8b5167da","tid":1050784,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"一定要玩QI ? 其實用膠都可以， 唔係個個人要無線充電， 而且用膠輕好多"},{"pid":"f945e645c7d230d9d9a02f0423b0d2e9bffd44a0","tid":1050784,"uid":73310,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:43:08.000Z","msg":"***dog ：總之摺mon係我地出先啦，理得我出舊垃圾半製成品膠面mon，你遲出就係你已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71572cec2ecd82ab949d39eb08d8e418fa03e44","tid":1050784,"uid":26332,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"5486b09ce34b2bf386e9e4e0adc5759e8b5167da","tid":1050784,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"一定要玩QI ? 其實用膠都可以， 唔係個個人要無線充電， 而且用膠輕好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"戴錶你都唔會揀膠錶啦，iphone用膠真係好核突"},{"pid":"da1fcdc402df9192a886f2ecf975d63eb8bfa303","tid":1050784,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:51:12.000Z","msg":"康寧出嘅話，apple 用得，各他廠的應該用得"},{"pid":"428bf68af4ef0ddf9cd3cbec8ef712d23fe2bea7","tid":1050784,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"可能唔係電話用，係手錶用呢"},{"pid":"9b0bcc7bddc1e9179c1e3a918f7fff8edc56abd3","tid":1050784,"uid":55951,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54pOHvd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54pOHvd.jpg&h=8684262f&s={SIZE}\" /><b